OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWindfall tax to end if     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fenergy prices drop         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The windfall tax on oil and gas firms  
OL,6, will be scrapped if prices fall to     
OL,7, normal levels for a sustained period,  
OL,8, the government has announced.          
OL,10,FHalting the windfall tax would cut the 
OL,11,Foverall tax rate on energy firms from  
OL,12,F75% to 40%.                            
OL,14,FA windfall tax is used to target firms 
OL,15,Fwhich benefit from something they were 
OL,16,Fnot responsible for.                   
OL,18,FIt was introduced last year to help    
OL,19,Ffund a scheme to lower energy bills for
OL,20,Fhouseholds and businesses.             
